Good boy, Fu Bao.

48
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:28,710
Fu Bao.

49
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,710
Excuse me!

50
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:30,400
Fu Bao.

51
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:31,680
Careful.

52
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,630
Excuse me!

53
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:41,970
Wan'er?

54
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:43,910
Wan'er!

55
00:03:43,910 --> 00:03:45,520
Candied Haws! Come and take a look.

56
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:46,150
Wan'er!

57
00:03:46,710 --> 00:03:47,630
Lord Ling.

58
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,430
Lord Ling!

59
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,590
Please behave yourself.

60
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:55,560
Wan'er,

61
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,840
everything I did with Niyue before

62
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,750
was just an act.

63
00:03:59,120 --> 00:04:00,470
I was tricking her to get the antidote.

64
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,870
Regardless of the truth,

65
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:09,800
I no longer care.

66
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,080
Wan'er,

67
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,360
I shouldn't have been presumptuous.

68
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,830
I shouldn't have kept it from you,

69
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,160
and I definitely shouldn't
have broken your heart.

70
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,560
The damage has been done.

71
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,160
No matter what you say, it's useless.

72
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,480
You should know,

73
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,000
some things are lost forever

74
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,720
once missed.

75
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,240
But we can still start over again.

76
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,510
Wan'er,

77
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:30,270
will you give me another chance?

78
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,070
If you continue to pester me,

79
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,600
I will jump off the bridge.

80
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:38,700
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

81
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,310
Do you really want
nothing to do with me?

82
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:43,800
That's right.

83
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:46,190
You and I have long severed ties.

84
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:47,830
From now on,

85
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,800
