93
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,390
that he won't give up easily?

94
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,240
If he gave up,

95
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,680
he wouldn't be Ling Xiao.

96
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,800
Fu Bao's hundredth day birthday
is coming up.

97
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,000
When he calculates the days,

98
00:05:55,270 --> 00:05:57,190
he'll realize you were lying

99
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,240
about having a child with me.

100
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:01,680
We need to prepare early.

101
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,560
All right. I'll do as you say.

102
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,750
Thank you.

103
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:07,600
You don't need to feel burdened.

104
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:08,870
I'm willing to do this.

105
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,070
My Lord,

106
00:06:23,720 --> 00:06:24,680
