109
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:32,040
Her Ladyship...

110
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:33,600
I mean,

111
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:35,630
Su Wan'er really has
remarried Jing Tian.

112
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,040
And Fu Bao is about
to turn one month old.

113
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:37,950
If we count the days...

114
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:38,800
If we count the days,

115
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,270
she gave herself to him

116
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:43,950
shortly after leaving me.

117
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,870
My Lord, there are plenty
of women in the world.

118
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,680
But there's only one Su Wan'er
in the world.

119
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:52,190
Go, send a letter
to Jing Tian in secret.

120
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,600
Yes, My Lord.

121
