She has become thin.

122
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,510
Her face

123
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:02,600
is also as pale as snow.

124
00:07:03,210 --> 00:07:04,220
I suppose you know

125
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:07,270
