126
00:07:10,430 --> 00:07:11,800
If you can't take care of her properly,

127
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:15,190
I don't mind looking after her for you.

128
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,190
I don't need others

129
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,040
