136
00:07:50,070 --> 00:07:51,160
You are really willing

137
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,870
to let me have

138
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:54,070
such a great credit?

139
00:07:57,310 --> 00:07:58,750
I just want her to live well.

140
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,750
Wan'er,

141
00:08:11,950 --> 00:08:13,000
I found a great doctor

142
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,190
and got a new prescription for you.

143
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,360
Take it now.

144
00:08:32,750 --> 00:08:34,200
This medicine is strange.

145
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,550
