148
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:43,080
I'm feeling better off

149
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,150
and much warmer.

150
00:08:44,510 --> 00:08:45,360
Jing Tian,

151
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:47,390
